info.name: Together1 API
info.description:
Collection to test Together1 Server-Side API

You must first get a token to authenticate to the API.  You can use the collection's authorization tab to request a token. Tokens usually last 24 hours.

Also, "Get All Classes" extracts some return values into environment variables for use in other tests.

request.description:
This is used mostly for testing purposes.

item.name: Get My Upcoming Session - Later Today

request.description:
Get classes and sessions that I can participate in soon.  For instructors, these are any classes that have sessions that I am the instructor for, and for the participate, these are classes that I am participating in.  

Only sessions that start instruction within a specified number of hours (see 'hours' parameter) are returned. The default number of hours is 2
